    {
      "id": "03d13a9c-bd12-4dfe-ba51-049ec3d9645d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Current models to predict academic performance focus on attributes of the students but not the relationships between the students themselves. Authors propose a multi-view Hypergraph neural network to address this issue:",
